    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and practical ride! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest character from its time on the road, but it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone needing reliable transportation. It\u2019s been well-maintained to ensure it stays road-ready, making it a fantastic value for a driver who prioritizes utility and a smooth commute. Come see why this honest, hard-working car is the perfect fit for your daily needs!",
      "price": 19500.0,
