    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a dedicated restoration project or a donor car for parts. The body has widespread rust, particularly around the wheel wells and rocker panels, along with several deep dents and a failing clear coat. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips, indicating that major repairs are necessary before it can be considered roadworthy. The interior also shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics.",
      "price": 4200.0,
